msgid "Projects"
msgstr "Projekt"

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: C/projects.page:8
msgid ""
"A Graphs project file saves the complete state of your work so you can close "
"it and pick up exactly where you left off. All project actions are available "
"from the application menu."
msgstr ""
"En Graphs-projektfil sparar det fullständiga tillståndet för ditt arbete så "
